  <entry>
    <title>这是一场美丽的邂逅</title>
    <url>/2016/08/30/a-beautiful-encounter/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h4 id="这是一场美丽的邂逅"><a href="#这是一场美丽的邂逅" class="headerlink" title="这是一场美丽的邂逅"></a>这是一场美丽的邂逅</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是一场美丽的邂逅</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">都说</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">恋爱要从 看电影开始，从牵手发芽🌱</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">不做过一场，怎么体会呢？</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">“使徒行者” </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">我们一起看的第一场电影</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">可谓里外都是戏，就没怎么专注看[偷笑]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">只想陪着她。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">不知道是影厅空口 不给面？还是太给力？</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">硬是把微风吹成了冷风[摊手]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">凉嗖嗖的，找了几次工作人员，可就是没胆子给她取暖😂</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">好在是夏天，不然非得理论理论</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">看了电影，自然就少不了影评：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">先说说演员阵容 </span><br><span class="line">古天乐，张家辉，吴镇宇，佘诗曼，还真个个是大腕儿</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">几乎不用想，电影讲的就是香港警匪</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">虽然 今天才知道张家辉长啥样?😂 </span><br><span class="line">嘿嘿，那咱也不怕掉份，谁知道我不知道呢[摊手]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这部剧吧</span><br><span class="line">伏笔很多，但不够走心 </span><br><span class="line">演技很高，但槽点太低 </span><br><span class="line">没有惊心动魄的打斗场面 </span><br><span class="line">也没层出不穷的段子笑料 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">笑料！ 笑料 ！今天我最最需要的！[捂脸]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">唯一的看点，也就阿蓝用生命掩护小英时的眼神</span><br><span class="line">这个真要赞！打动我了 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">都说冲着人性而去，但最终带着“尼玛”回来 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">不过还好，角色塑造的还不错</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">活泼老辣的丁小嘉 </span><br><span class="line">漂亮痴情的小英 </span><br><span class="line">生死关头的俩兄弟 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">更重要的是</span><br><span class="line">剧外还有我那活泼可爱的小徒弟，陪着她，就够了</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- 2016年8月30日 万泰城</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://soilove.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/32e/live/her.png"></p>
]]></content>
